longBusinessSummary: ITC Hotels Limited engages in the operation of hotels and resorts. It operates under the ITC Hotels, Mementos, Storii, Welcomhotel, Fortune, and WelcomHeritage brands. The company was founded in 1975 and is based in Gurugram, India.
